{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-classic\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-undefined=\"%7B%22path%22%3A%5B%5B5%2C0%2C0%5D%2C%5B5%2C0%2C0%5D%5D%2C%22active%22%3Atrue%7D\"><p data-lake-id=\"e98cd7ff553e2783c88799b47222f1b2\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #121212;\"><span>https</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">在1994年首次提出，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">2000年代末至2010年代初，HTTPS开始广泛使用；</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"a20d224c568e48b9d67847a2c66a8c01_p_0\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #121212;\">https中的s表示SSL或者TLS，就是在原http的基础上加上一层用于数据加密、解密、身份认证的安全层。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"0f11b4e03c976e6e55ffe4875beba2b4\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">HTTPS开发的主要目的，是提供对</span>网站<span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">服务器的</span>身份认证<span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">，保护交换资料的隐私与</span>完整性<span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">。</span></p><blockquote style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); opacity: 0.6;\"><p data-lake-id=\"681e7ac57559ec3d0432d8f5510ce693\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><strong>传输层安全性协议</strong><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">（英语：</span><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\"><strong>T</strong>ransport <strong>L</strong>ayer <strong>S</strong>ecurity</span><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">，缩写：</span><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\"><strong>TLS</strong></span><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">）及其前身</span><strong>安全套接层</strong><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">（英语：</span><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\"><strong>S</strong>ecure <strong>S</strong>ockets <strong>L</strong>ayer</span><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">，缩写：</span><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\"><strong>SSL</strong></span><span class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-size: 15px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 15px\">）</span>是一种安全协议，目的是为互联网通信提供安全及数据完整性保障</p></blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"b19683aaf2955b1bfe257f326a4c7b16\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-